INSERT INTO `tb_test_item` VALUES ('214', '<p>Question 191-195 refer to the following notice and review</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>The Indian Star</p>\r\n<p>Shooting of Bear Lake on hold</p>\r\n<p>Premier delayed</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>The hightly anticipated premier of Bear Lake, a film directed by Raj Patal, has been delayed from early November to late spring. This delay is a result of bad weather and location selection. As well, many of the animal scenes have been talking longer to shoot than expected. These factors, combined with a sagging economy, caused the delay. Representatives for the film, however, have emphatically stated that filming resume soon.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Movie Review: Bear Lake</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Mountain Films is pound to announce its anticipated release of Bear Lake this week, after eight months of delay. The Raj Patal film is an adaptation of the Pulitzer Prize-winning novel of the same name. The novel is an epic love story, based in the foothills of nothern India, with many twist and turns.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>The adaptation of a prize-winning novel to the big screen can be very difficult, because for every reader the character and the scenes will have been imagined differently. As well, it can be difficult to select the proper scense to shoot and ultimately include in the film. But after watching this film I belive Raj Patal has done it againn! I feel this was achieved because of the collaboration between Samir Rajeet and Patl, who managed to bring the book to life beautiful, It is rumored that the pair will be working together again soon.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Patal has show many times in the past that he capable of depicting the lives of everyday people and the relationships that they have. Bear Lake is a giant step forward for Patal’s career because of the amount of funding and publicity that it has received. He used this money wisely, producing breathtaking cinematography and moving love scenes. This movie’s success was also greathly anhanced by thr performances give by Deepark Shakur and Latanji apur.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>The limited release of Bear Lake opens Friday night and will go into wide release at the end of the month.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '9', '1', '3', 'The director and author have different visions.', 'Details from the book must be left out of the film', 'Readers have already visualized the characters', 'There is more dialogue in the films than in books', '<p>According to the writer, what is difficult about turning a book into a movie?</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '191', '0', '1', '1', 'vi', '0', '2015-10-22 12:53:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
