INSERT INTO `tb_test_item` VALUES ('401', '<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"319\">\r\n<p>168. What is the purpose of this letter?</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>To book a reservation at the hotel</li>\r\n<li>To send out invitations</li>\r\n<li>To arrange a meeting</li>\r\n<li>To confirm a reservation</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>169. By what date will Mr. Sams need to be informed of the number of guests?</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>November 10</li>\r\n<li>November 11</li>\r\n<li>November 24</li>\r\n<li>November 25</li>\r\n</ol></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"319\">\r\n<p>170. What does Mr. Sams promise to send to Ms. Goldstein?</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>A reservation list</li>\r\n<li>A deposit slip</li>\r\n<li>A list of names</li>\r\n<li>A list of possible meals</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>171. What is NOT included in the letter?</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>The date of the event</li>\r\n<li>Mr.Sams’ contact information</li>\r\n<li>Mr. Sams’ address</li>\r\n<li>The fax number for Best Eastern Star Hotel</li>\r\n</ol></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Questions 172- 176 </strong>refer to the following articles</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 210px; width: 963px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"638\">\r\n<p>Last night, in a quiet ceremony it was announced that Ivan Gorelikov won this year’s Escalade Award for his book <em>The Matterhorn. </em>He is the best known for his spy- based action thriller <em>The End Game</em>, which will soon be made into a movie starring Jim Bates. “I am more surprised than anyone!” exclaimed Gorelikov with a giant smile. “I am ust happy that people enjoy my writing.”</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>The young writer, who is just 30 years old, has already published 10 books, andwon a few minor writing awards but he has never enjoyed winning an award like this. Gorelikov was the youngest writer to win the Silver Leaflet Award for his second book in the series. His books have quickly become common household names and are considered must- reads by the spy- book genre crowd. Gorelikov came from a poor family, with one sister, in a small town outside of Moscow. His father was a factory worker who saide this about his son, “All I ever wanted for my son was a good education, but he has done so much with it. I couldn’t be more proud of him!” Ivan Gorelikovis currently working on a compilation of poetry <em>Higher Life </em>that he says, “was made just for me”.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>The Escalade Award is presented every year to an author who writes books that show promise in the spy genre. Last year’s award was given to Neil Stratus for his book called <em>The Aprroach</em>which has now sold over 5 million copies worldwide.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '9', '2', '2', 'His family was rich growing up', 'He was surprised to win the Escalade Award', 'He was born in California', 'He writes romance novels', '<p>What is true about Gorelikov?</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '172', '0', '1', '1', 'vi', '1', '2015-10-24 14:45:32', '2015-10-24 22:22:13');
