INSERT INTO `tb_test_item` VALUES ('1763', '<p>Question 173- 177</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Date: September 12</p>\r\n<p>To: All Hanover Employees</p>\r\n<p>From: Julie Lewis, Marketing Director</p>\r\n<p>Re: New Enviromental Policy</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Dear Hanover employees,</p>\r\n<p>Thank you very much for offering your suggestions on how Hanover, Inc. can improve its enviromental policy. As you are aware, our clothing company began as a family- owned business that quickly grew into an international distributor. In appreciation for our financial success, we would like to establish our company as a model for the industry and have decided to do so by improving our enviroment policies. Our new enviromental initiative is designed to save the company money and also reduce the amount of waste that we produce. Based on the more than 100 entries that employees submitted, we have come up with three main ways of doing so:</p>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"366\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>IDEA</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"272\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>SUBMITTED BY</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"366\">\r\n<p>Send electronic copies instead of paper ones whenever possible</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"272\">\r\n<p>Roger Waters</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"366\">\r\n<p>Put lights on times in order to reduce electricity</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"272\">\r\n<p>Cynthia Dale</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"366\">\r\n<p>Walk to work or take public transportation</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"272\">\r\n<p>Eugene Phillips</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Congratulations to Roger, Cynthia, and Eugene for their wonderful and \"green\" ideas. These three employees will now have the opportunity to win a brand new hybrid car.</p>\r\n<p>We need your help to decide which idea is the best. Please vote for your favorite by visiting <a href=\"http://www.hanover/greenideas.com\">www.hanover/greenideas.com</a>. Please enter your employee number and password, and follow the directions to choose your favorite idea. You can begin voting on September 14 and you must vote by noon on September 21. You may vote only one time. The winning idea will be announced on September 30, when the winner will be announced at our annual fall conference.</p>\r\n<p>If you have further comments or questions about the competition, please call me at 789- 877- 8098</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your time and participation.</p>\r\n<p>Julie Lewis</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '9', '11', '3', 'Submit a new policy', 'Fill out a questionaire', 'Help choose a winner', 'Change their password', '<p><strong>What does Julie Lewis ask employees to do?</strong></p>', '173', '0', '1', '1', 'vi', '1', '2015-11-28 15:15:04', '2015-11-30 15:21:56');
