ducts.</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Tuesday, June 9, 8:30~11:00 a.m</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Cost $55</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"604\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">REGISTRATION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Name: <em>Charles Salazar</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Address: <em>432 W. State St, Albany, NY </em>12123</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Phone No: (201) 928-1921</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>E-mail: <em><a href=\"mailto:salazar1@mail.com\">salazar1@mail.com</a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Workshop Number: 1</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Date: January 3</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Comments: <em>My department would like to send 5 of its members to the workshop on March 7. Are we eligible for a group discount?</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p> </p>', '9', '19', '2', 'To ask for new workshop ideas', 'To promote upcomning workshops', 'To inform business owners of previous workshops', 'To modify the workshop schedule', '<p><strong></strong><strong>What is the purpose of the announcement?</strong></p>', '181', '0', '1', '1', 'vi', '0', '2015-12-29 19:05:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
