INSERT INTO `tb_test_item` VALUES ('3859', '<p>Question 165- 167</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>To: Barbara Moore &lt;bmoore@juindustries.com&gt;</p>\r\n<p>From: Vince Miller &lt;vmiller@juindustries.com&gt;</p>\r\n<p>Date: Wednesday, April 20, 9:00 am</p>\r\n<p>Subject: Tonight &rsquo; s meeting in Los Angeles</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>I am sorry to give you such late notice, but I need to postpone our early afternoon meeting today until later this week. Arie Gold, our leading agent, has booked us a meeting later today with Quinton Jones, the famous director from Detroit, about his upcoming movie Aquaman. On top of that, I have an executive producer meeting with the studio and with the president of operations in Hollywood. I have free time on Friday morning at around 11. Is that time good for you? If that is not a good time for you, please tell me a more suitable date and time. I am looking forward to meeting you and your client.</p>\r\n<p>Vince</p>', '9', '21', '1', 'To postpone a meeting', 'To confirm a meeting', 'To arrange a meeting with Quinton Jones', 'To talk about making a movie', '<p>What  &rsquo; s the purpose of the e- mail?</p>', '165', '0', '1', '1', 'vi', '0', '2016-01-01 15:32:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
