INSERT INTO `tb_test_item` VALUES ('4077', '<p>Question 191-195</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Dear Mr. Heckelman</p>\r\n<p>I am a restaurateur in Poland, planning to open a new restaurant Bon Jour in Warsaw, Poland soon. I think your new product line would be good for my kitchen, and would like to obtain more information on it.</p>\r\n<p>I was searching for a reliable and affordable kitchen equipment supplier and the manager of La Fete recommended your company to me because your company is well known for quality products and international shipping service. I need the following items for my kitchen:</p>\r\n<p>- 10 aluminum sheet pans</p>\r\n<p>- 10 aluminum saucepans</p>\r\n<p>- 5 steamer baskets- 20qt</p>\r\n<p>- 3 round food warmers- over 10qt</p>\r\n<p>The restaurant will be open in five months, and I should decide which kitchen equipment supplier to use within two weeks so that I can purchase all the supplies I need in time. Please send me your product list and cost estimate as soon as possible. I would also like to receive information on bulk order discounts and international shipping policy.</p>\r\n<p>Best regards,</p>\r\n<p>Huelle</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Hendrix Restaurant Equipment &amp; Supplies</p>\r\n<p>Full size aluminum sheet pan (12- pack) E68 (E7 ea)</p>\r\n<p>- Heavy duty 3003 aluminum</p>\r\n<p>- Rolled edge for extra durability</p>\r\n<p>- Restaurant quality</p>\r\n<p>- Great for baking rolls, cookies, brownies, buns or any type of baking use</p>\r\n<p>- Dimensions: 26” x18” x1”</p>\r\n<p>5.50 qt aluminum saucepan E6.5 ea.</p>\r\n<p>- Satin finish</p>\r\n<p>- Dent- resistant</p>\r\n<p>- 3mm thickness</p>\r\n<p>- Flat bottom for even heat</p>\r\n<p>- NSF listed</p>\r\n<p>Aluminum cylindrical steamer basket- 20qt.E10</p>\r\n<p>- Perforated holes</p>\r\n<p>- Fits inside stock pots</p>\r\n<p>- Easy to lift pail handle</p>\r\n<p>- Smooth mirror finish</p>\r\n<p>- Use for seafood, vegetables of deep- fried turkey</p>\r\n<p>Wells roud countertop food warmers- 11qt.E100</p>\r\n<p>- Anodized aluminum pot and band heating element</p>\r\n<p>- Efficient heat distribution</p>\r\n<p>- Wet and dry operation</p>\r\n<p>- Thermostatic controls (Temperature range from room to 100  °C.</p>\r\n<p>Shipping rate: Domestic E7, International E15</p>\r\n<p>Discounts offered for 10 items or more</p>', '9', '23', '3', 'They are not available in a local store', 'They were advertised on TV', 'They were recommend by a colleague', 'They are used by famous people', '<p>According to the email, why does Ms. Huelle want to purchase Hendrix’s kitchen products?</p>', '191', '0', '1', '1', 'vi', '0', '2016-01-05 15:07:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
